  "prompt": "What is the best answer I can give my girl when she asks me how are you?",
  "response": "The best answer can vary depending on your relationship and how you genuinely feel. Here are a few options that balance honesty and charm:\n\n1. **Simple and Honest:** \"I'm doing well, thanks for asking! How about you?\"\n2. **Playful:** \"I'm great! But my day would be even better if I could spend it with you.\"\n3. **Thoughtful:** \"I've been good, just been thinking about how lucky I am to have you in my life.\"\n4. **Cheerful:** \"Feeling good! Just excited to talk to you. How's your day going?\"\n\nChoose an answer that feels natural to you and matches your relationship dynamic!",
